 em-md-4 feature"><div class="low-padding"><div class="feature-image"><img src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/icons/seizure_detection.svg" alt="Seizure Detection"></div><div class="feature-title title-color bold min-margin-bottom">1. Seizure Detection</div><div class="feature-description">Embrace continuously collects your physiological data via its sensors. The data are analyzed in real-time using Embrace’s advanced machine learning, to try to detect unusual events like convulsive seizures.</div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-12 em-md-4 feature"><div class="low-padding"><div class="feature-image"><img src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/icons/alert_dispatch.svg" alt="Alert Dispatching"></div><div class="feature-title title-color bold min-margin-bottom">2. Alert Dispatching</div><div class="feature-description">The Alert App is connected to your Embrace via Bluetooth®, and is automatically activated when Embrace detects a convulsive seizure. The App will send an alert notification (SMS and phone call) to your Caregivers using the smartphone’s cellular data or Wi-Fi connection.</div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-12 em-md-4 feature"><div class="low-padding"><div class="feature-image"><img src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/icons/caregiver_notification.svg" alt="Caregiver Alert"></div><div class="feature-title title-color bold min-margin-bottom">3. Caregiver Alert</div><div class="feature-description">The Embrace Alert System notifies your Caregivers simultaneously. Caregivers only need a phone with cellular signal to receive these notifications, no smartphone required.</div></div></div></div><div class="low-margin-top low-padding-left low-padding-right note"><div class="text-center">Important: Both Bluetooth® and either an Internet or cellular data connection are necessary for the Alert App to send calls and SMS when Embrace detects a convulsive seizure</div><div class="text-center low-margin-top"><a href="https://support.empatica.com/hc/en-us/sections/200817625-Research-and-Medical" title="Learn more about Embrace seizure detection capabilities">Learn more about Embrace seizure detection capabilities</a></div></div></div></div><div class="section-separator"></div><div class="section alert-system"><h2 class="text-center">Get the Most Out of the Alert App</h2><div class="text-center-xs"><div class="row"><div class="em-xs-12 em-md-8 em-md-offset-2"><div class="row low-margin-bottom"><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-6 em-sm-push-6"><img class="img-full-width lazyload" src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/alert/location-ldpi.jpg" data-src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/alert/location-xhdpi.jpg" alt="Alert Location"></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-6 em-sm-pull-6"><div class="no-padding-xs low-padding-right"><div class="title min-margin-top-xs">Alerts with Location<span class="apex">*</span></div><p>Enhance alerts with your precise GPS location to expedite assistance without hassle.</p><p class="text-small red-color min-margin-top"><span class="apex">*</span>Only available with Standard and Plus Subscription plans.</p></div></div></div><div class="row low-margin-bottom"><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-6"><img class="img-full-width lazyload" src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/alert/rest_mode-ldpi.jpg" data-src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/alert/rest_mode-xhdpi.jpg" alt="Rest Mode"></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-6"><div class="no-padding-xs low-padding-left"><div class="title min-margin-top-xs">Rest Mode<span class="apex">*</span></div><p>Take advantage of an additional seizure detection mode designed for use during periods of rest, such as reading or taking a nap.</p><p class="text-small red-color min-margin-top"><span class="apex">*</span>Only available with Standard and Plus Subscription plans.</p></div></div></div><div class="row low-margin-bottom"><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-6 em-sm-push-6"><img class="img-full-width lazyload" src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/alert/manage_caregivers-ldpi.jpg" data-src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/alert/manage_caregivers-xhdpi.jpg" alt="Alert Caregivers"></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-6 em-sm-pull-6"><div class="no-padding-xs low-padding-right"><div class="title min-margin-top-xs">Manage Caregivers<span class="apex">*</span></div><p>Ensure you always have someone ready to help. Activate and deactivate caregivers as you go about your day.</p><p class="text-small red-color min-margin-top"><span class="apex">*</span>Unlimited caregivers are available with Plus plan.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="section-separator"></div><div class="section"><h2 class="text-center no-margin-xs">Tailored Plans for your Needs</h2><div class="subscription-plans"><div class="row"><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-4"><div class="subscription-plan"><div class="subscription-plan-icon"><img src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/subscription/plan_lite.svg"></div><div class="subscription-plan-name">Lite</div><div class="subscription-plan-daily-price">$<h1>0.33</h1>/day</div><div class="subscription-plan-monthly-price">$9.90/month</div><div class="subscription-plan-description">Ideal if you have a single caregiver and want the benefit of seizure detection.</div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-4"><div class="subscription-plan selected"><div class="subscription-plan-icon"><img src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/subscription/plan_standard.svg"></div><div class="subscription-plan-name">Standard <span class="badge">Most Popular</span></div><div class="subscription-plan-daily-price">$<h1>0.65</h1>/day</div><div class="subscription-plan-monthly-price">$19.90/month</div><div class="subscription-plan-description">From Alert Location to Rest Mode, choose this plan if you want to take your Embrace to the next level.</div></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-4"><div class="subscription-plan"><div class="subscription-plan-icon"><img src="https://www.empatica.com/assets