      })
    }</script></div><div class="banner banner-section"><img class="lazyload banner-image hidden-xs" src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/alert/section_sudep-lg-ldpi.jpg" data-src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/alert/section_sudep-lg-xhdpi.jpg" alt="SUDEP"> <img class="lazyload banner-image visible-xs" src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/alert/section_sudep-sm-ldpi.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/alert/section_sudep-sm-hdpi.jpg 1x, https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/alert/section_sudep-sm-xhdpi.jpg 2x" alt="SUDEP"><div class="banner-content banner-content-right banner-content-middle"><div class="middle-wrapper"><div class="middle-content"><h2>More people die of SUDEP (Sudden Unexpected Death in Epilepsy) than of house fires every year.</h2><div class="low-margin-top">But every home has a smoke detector. Now, you too can alert your caregivers for prompt assistance when you need it.</div><div class="min-margin-top text-small">Source: <a href="http://www.epilepsy.com/learn/about-epilepsy-basics/facts-about-seizures-and-epilepsy" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Epilepsy Foundation</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="section no-padding section-buy-now"><div class="text-center visible-xs"><h2 class="no-margin">Make It Yours</h2></div><div class="row low-margin-bottom embrace-showcase visible-xs revert-margin-left revert-margin-right"><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-2 em-sm-offset-1"><div class="min-padding low-padding-xs min-padding-sm low-padding-left low-padding-right"><img class="lazyload img-full-width" src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/products/embrace_milan_black-ldpi.jpg" data-src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/images/products/embrace_milan_black-xhdpi.jpg" alt="Embrace Milan Black"></div></div><div class="em-xs-12 em-sm-2"><div class="min-padding low-padding-xs min-padding-sm low-padding-left low-padding-right"><img class="lazyload img-full-width" src="https://www.empatica.com/assets/image